        "heading-1-1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Timeless garments to dress your inner spirit",
            "heading_font_size": "heading-medium",
            "padding_bottom": 16,
            "heading_tag": "automatic"
          }
        },
        "text-1-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>From the depths of the Indonesian islands, where the spirit of volcanoes meets the power of oceans, nature bestows plants with its life-giving energy. Here, every breath of the earth is imbued with the strength of the elements. <br/><br/> Local artisans, with deep reverence, gather the gifts of this generous land: leaves, roots, and flowers. They unite them with the five elements — water, fire, earth, air, and ether — to create unique natural dyes, infusing fabrics with the essence of living nature.  <br/><br/>AYA creates a space where ancient traditions are reborn, and every thread absorbs the wisdom of the ages. This is a craft where time slows, allowing culture to thrive once more.  <br/><br/>With care and devotion, artisans handcraft sacred patterns — codes of elevated states. These patterns awaken the fabrics, transforming garments into vessels that support harmony and balance throughout the day.  <br/><br/>Before choosing your AYA garment, ask yourself: what state of being do you wish to embody today? <br/><br/><strong>Each piece is an Avatar — a reflection of your spirit, designed to reveal your essence.</strong></p>",
            "text_font_size": "body-medium",
            "padding_bottom": 16
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading-1-1",
