            "image_shape": "normal",
            "title": "aya community",
            "heading_font_size": "heading-small",
            "text": "<p>We witness AYA Sacred Wear traveling across the world — adorning the planet through weddings, sacred ceremonies, meaningful gatherings, and unforgettable encounters.</p><p>It is a profound miracle for us to see our creations become part of life’s most important moments.</p><p>To dress this planet, to accompany love, celebration, and connection, is our greatest honor.</p>",
