        "image-2": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/IMG_6393.jpg",
            "image_width": 100,
            "image_shape": "normal",
            "title": "sustainable materials",
            "heading_font_size": "heading-small",
            "text": "<p>Made in the very heart of beautiful Bali island by loving hands of local artisans. </p><p>AYA especially focus on fabrics that are hand-spun and hand-woven, supporting ancient skills and traditional crafts. Thriving to go deeper to the source of all the materials - from the seed planted to the people who weave the fabric. Our vision is to be able to connect with each being involved in the making from the very source.</p><p>Being able to Source the most ethical, fair trade, Eco and conscious materials</p>",
            "text_font_size": "body-medium",
            "button_text": "",
            "button_url": "",
            "button_type": "btn--primary hero__btn",
            "button_size": "",
            "button_style": "btn--solid",
            "show_arrow": false,
            "image_aspect_ratio": 1,
            "mobile_image_aspect_ratio": 1,
            "heading_tag": "automatic"
          }
        },
        "image-3": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/2-2.jpg",
            "image_width": 100,
            "image_shape": "normal",
            "title": "giving back",
            "heading_font_size": "heading-small",
            "text": "<p>All AYA Sacred Wear production is rooted in Bali.</p><p>We collaborate closely with local artisans, family-run workshops, and village communities — from handwoven fabrics and natural dyeing to handcrafted accessories and finishing details.<br/></p><p>By producing locally, we actively support livelihoods, preserve traditional skills, and contribute to the wellbeing of the communities behind each piece.</p><p>Every garment carries the hands, stories, and care of the people who create it — transforming craftsmanship into a shared, living exchange..<br/><br/></p><p>AYA Sacred Wear is a living community, and we are always open to conscious collaborations, shared visions, and creative exchanges.</p>",
            "text_font_size": "body-medium",
            "button_text": "",
            "button_url": "",
